creator: Various
description:
LibriVox recording of Long Poems Collection 008 by Various.
Read in English by Tony Addison; Ed Humpal; Newgatenovelist; Michele Fry; Peter Tucker; John Burlinson; Urban Bard
LibriVox’s Long Poems Collection 008: a collection of 14 public-domain poems longer than 10 minutes in length.
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
